------------------------
Introductory information
------------------------

Generated in neutral s1 configuration; semicore sp shells included.

Similar to a Na potential generated in the early 1990's by some member
of my group, probably D. King-Smith.

--------------------
Intended environment
--------------------

Mostly for Na in oxides where it is in the 1+ formal oxidation
state.

